text.div:
GenderStatus

This example value set defines a set of codes that can be used to indicate the current state of the animal's reproductive organs.

This value set defines it's own terms in the system http://hl7.org/fhir/animal-genderstatus

CodeDisplayDefinition
neuteredNeuteredThe animal has been castrated and is infertile
intactIntactThe animals reproductive organs are intact
